{"word":"H4058 - מָדַד - mâdad - maw-dad' - Measure","slug":"H4058","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָדַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâdad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-dad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Measure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D3;&#x05D3; - ma&#x0302;dad</b> - <i>maw-dad'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>stretch</i>; by implication to <i>measure</i> (as if by <i>stretching</i> a line); figuratively to <i>be extended: - </i>measure, mete, stretch self."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4055\">H4055</a>, <a href=\"#/H4059\">H4059</a>, <a href=\"#/H4060\">H4060</a>, <a href=\"#/H4067\">H4067</a>, <a href=\"#/H4081\">H4081</a>, <a href=\"#/H4461\">H4461</a>"}]}